# Incorrect Usage

**Error:** Unknown command non-existent for atmos

Valid subcommands are:

  • about
  • ai
  • ansible
  • atlantis
  • auth
  • aws
  • ci
  • completion
  • composition
  • container
  • describe
  • devcontainer
  • docs
  • emulator
  • env
  • git
  • helmfile
  • help
  • kubernetes
  • list
  • lsp
  • mcp
  • packer
  • pro
  • profile
  • secret
  • show
  • support
  • terraform
  • tf
  • tf-custom
  • theme
  • toolchain
  • validate
  • vendor
  • version
  • workflow

## Usage

 atmos [flags]
 atmos [sub-command] [flags]

## Hints

💡 Run atmos --help for usage
